{"tid":1438845,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国想玩貨幣戰？  納瓦羅：美將採取「強硬行動」反擊","createTime":"2019-08-10T02:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T02:20:41.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6ab7d85d4858927b5c50a1b1f1e4eddc61f8a27e","tid":1438845,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:04:16.000Z","msg":"白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅（Peter Navarro）週五指出，中國打算繼續貶值人民幣來取得優勢，他警告若中國再這麼做，美國將採取強硬行動應對。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦羅週五於《CNBC》節目表示：「很明顯，中國正在貿易戰中操縱貨幣匯率，若他們再繼續這麼做，我們將採取強硬行動來反擊。」<br />\n<br />\n本週稍早，中國將人民幣中間價定在2008年4月以來的新低，納瓦羅也呼應政府將中國列為「匯率操縱國」，他指出：「中國已將人民幣貶值10%以上，目的是為了緩衝關稅帶來的影響。」<br />\n<br />\n對於中國停購美農產品的報復，納瓦羅表示所有美農將團結起來，而不受中國的侵害。他也強調，不像美國的消費者，中國消費者將因美國祭出的關稅飽受苦頭。納瓦羅表示，中國操縱匯率還將產品降價，最終將承擔所有後果，受到的損害將遠遠超過美國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2880031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2880031&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVVRUXPbyrNnFnNFpNAJjDn8%3D&h=b1dd5512\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2880031&h=c643a944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2880031</a>"},{"pid":"9670ac300bb95a5c66d9c4fca50f1b40881ae477","tid":1438845,"uid":61653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:06:59.000Z","msg":"美軍來了"},{"pid":"dce959f6f53b7caf4df8fd1c0d047a90a30f3c97","tid":1438845,"uid":36178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:07:04.000Z","msg":"打貨幣戰開正美國果瓣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138d0afc4178e8fd13a6767bd974be6a4cc160f1","tid":1438845,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:20:41.000Z","msg":"覺得依家中国好似老鼠咁 俾人打到走投無路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}